ChatSpammer for WoW 1.12
Usage:

/run ChatSpammerStart(text, channel, interval, amount)

text - text to spam
channel - [optional] channel where to spam, either a name or a number. Default: "world"
interval - [optional] interval in seconds between messages. Default: 60
amount - [optional] amount of times to spam or -1 for no limit. Default: -1

Ex. 
/run ChatSpammerStart("LFM BRD, need tank", "world", 60, 5) - spams "LFM BRD, need tank" message in world channel every minute 5 times total
/run ChatSpammerStart("LFM BRD, need tank", 2, 30) - spams "LFM BRD, need tank" message in channel number 2 every 30 seconds with no total message limit
/run ChatSpammerStart("LFM BRD, need tank", "say") - spams "LFM BRD, need tank" message in /say every minute with no  total message limit
/run ChatSpammerStart("LFM BRD, need tank") - spams "LFM BRD, need tank" message in world channel every minute with no total message limit


/run ChatSpammerStop()
Stops spamming prematurely
